room_title: Escape room "The Time Machine: Nemesis" by Dynamic Escape Rooms in Phoenix
room_address: 1797 W University Dr, Suite 168, Tempe AZ 85281
room_description:
Two powerful forces face each other across space and time. The fight for reality as we know it has begun and you are the only one that can prevent the most powerful weapon in the universe from falling into the hands of your most dangerous foe. 

     Lead your team to victory and fulfill your destiny before your nemesis does it first. The game is on!
